snippet.title: Endless Dungeon - Official Fassie: Hero Reveal Trailer | gamescom 2023
snippet.description:
Meet the hero, Fassie, learn about the character and see him in action in this latest trailer for Endless Dungeon, an upcoming squad-based tactical action rogue-lite game with a twist of tower defense. Endless Dungeon will be available on PC, Xbox Series X/S, Xbox One, PlayStation 4, PlayStation 5, and Nintendo Switch on October 19, 2023.

#IGN #Gaming
